  "pageTitle": "C&D 廢棄物回收管線手冊",
  "bodyHtml": "<main class=\"product-page resource-detail-page\">\n      <section class=\"section resource-detail-hero\" aria-labelledby=\"resource-title\">\n        <p class=\"eyebrow\">手冊</p>\n        <h1 id=\"resource-title\">C&D 廢棄物回收管線手冊</h1>\n        <p class=\"hero-copy\">為評估整合破碎、篩選、分離、打包及數位管理以回收C&amp;D廢棄物的產品概覽。</p>\n        <div class=\"resource-meta-row\" aria-label=\"資源元資料\">\n          <span>類型：產品手冊</span>\n          <span>更新：2026-06-30</span>\n          <span>買家合適度：C&amp;D與大型廢棄物專案</span>\n          <span>評論時間：10 min</span>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section resource-detail-layout\" aria-labelledby=\"coverage-title\">\n        <article class=\"resource-detail-panel\">\n          <h2 id=\"coverage-title\">本資源涵蓋內容</h2>\n          <ul class=\"feature-list\">\n            <li>支援 廢棄物類型：建築、裝飾、拆除與大宗廢棄物</li>\n            <li>從進料到輸出回收的核心製程模組</li>\n            <li>典型產出物如骨料、金屬、輕質材料及打包回收物</li>\n            <li>討論線路配置前需要專案意見</li>\n          </ul>\n        </article>\n        <aside class=\"resource-detail-panel\">\n          <h2>何時使用此資源</h2>\n          <p>評估新的C&amp;D廢棄物處理廠、升級現有分揀管線，或準備內部可行性審查時，請使用此手冊。</p>\n          <a class=\"primary-button\" href=\"/contact\">請求此資源</a>\n        </aside>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section\" aria-labelledby=\"related-title\">\n        <div class=\"section-heading\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">相關資源</p>\n          <h2 id=\"related-title\">規劃一個停止與死亡廢棄物專案</h2>\n          <p>在申請提案前，請先審查產品 詳情、服務 支援 及 RFQ 輸入。</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"resource-related-grid\">\n          <a href=\"/products/construction-waste-recycling-line\">\n            C&D 廢棄物產品頁面\n            <span class=\"resource-related-cta\" aria-hidden=\"true\">探索</span>\n          </a>\n          <a href=\"/resources/project-inquiry-checklist\">\n            專案調查檢查清單\n            <span class=\"resource-related-cta\" aria-hidden=\"true\">探索</span>\n          </a>\n          <a href=\"/service-support\">\n            服務 &amp; 支援\n            <span class=\"resource-related-cta\" aria-hidden=\"true\">探索</span>\n          </a>\n          <a href=\"/contact\">\n            傳送 專案 詳情\n            <span class=\"resource-related-cta\" aria-hidden=\"true\">探索</span>\n          </a>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n    </main>"
}
